983
01:05:20,660 --> 01:05:21,980
♫ Agar aku bisa merasakan cintamu cinta cinta cinta ♫

984
01:05:21,980 --> 01:05:23,390
Kenapa kamu tiba-tiba bertanya?

985
01:05:23,390 --> 01:05:26,010
Karena aku tiba-tiba penasaran.

986
01:05:26,010 --> 01:05:29,680
Itu mungkin–

